## 🧠 About Me

```
I'm a B.Tech (AI & Data Science) student and Java Full Stack Developer who enjoys
turning complex, ambiguous problems into clean, production-ready systems.

My core focus is backend engineering with Spring Boot and building end-to-end
full-stack applications — from REST APIs and relational database design to
responsive React front-ends. I care about writing code that is maintainable,
secure, and scalable, not just code that works.

Alongside full-stack development, I actively explore AI/ML and applied data
science, and I enjoy working across the entire product lifecycle — design,
development, debugging, and deployment.
```

**🎯 Open To:**
- Full Stack Developer / Java Developer roles (Fresher)
- Software Engineering internships & apprenticeships
- AI/ML collaborative projects
- Open source contributions

