## 🚀 Featured Projects

<details>
<summary><b>🏦 Marculix Banking System</b></summary>
<br/>

A full-stack banking system application built with a strong focus on secure transaction handling, modular architecture, and clean database design.

| Aspect | Details |
|---|---|
| **Stack** | Java, Spring Boot, PostgreSQL/JDBC, REST APIs |
| **Scale** | Multi-module banking workflows (accounts, transactions) |
| **Performance** | Optimized query handling via JDBC |
| **Security** | Layered validation, secure data handling |
| **Impact** | Core project demonstrating full-stack banking domain logic |
| **Repository** | [github.com/sarthakdingar5112](https://github.com/sarthakdingar5112) |

Designed to simulate real-world banking operations with clean separation between the data access layer, business logic, and presentation, emphasizing maintainable Spring architecture.

</details>

<details>
<summary><b>🎵 AI Music Generation App</b></summary>
<br/>

An application exploring AI-driven music generation, combining backend logic with generative techniques.

| Aspect | Details |
|---|---|
| **Stack** | Python / JavaScript, AI/ML libraries |
| **Scale** | Single-user generative application |
| **Performance** | Real-time / near real-time generation pipeline |
| **Security** | N/A (client-facing generative app) |
| **Impact** | Demonstrates applied AI beyond conventional CRUD apps |
| **Repository** | [github.com/sarthakdingar5112](https://github.com/sarthakdingar5112) |

Built to explore how generative AI models can be integrated into interactive applications, going beyond standard full-stack CRUD projects.

</details>

<details>
<summary><b>🧩 Roxiler Full Stack Challenge</b></summary>
<br/>

A role-based full-stack coding challenge submission featuring authenticated APIs and a React front-end.

| Aspect | Details |
|---|---|
| **Stack** | Node.js, Express, PostgreSQL, React.js |
| **Scale** | Full CRUD system with role-based access |
| **Performance** | RESTful API design with structured DB queries |
| **Security** | JWT-based authentication, bcrypt password hashing |
| **Impact** | End-to-end ownership of backend + frontend + auth |
| **Repository** | [github.com/sarthakdingar5112/roxiler-fullstack-challenge](https://github.com/sarthakdingar5112/roxiler-fullstack-challenge) |

Implemented secure, role-based authentication and authorization from scratch, connecting a Node/Express backend to a PostgreSQL database and a React front-end.

</details>

